<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/header.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Kc323vGBEqzTmouAECnVceyQqyqdsSiqLQISBL29aUW4U/M7pSPA/gEUZQqv1cwx4OnYxTxve5UMg5GT6L4JJg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <title>CSI</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs"); %>

    <div class="hero">
        <div class="Upper">
            <div class="title">
                <span>c</span>
                <span>s</span>
                <span>i</span>
            </div>
            <div class="title">
                <span>m</span>
                <span>i</span>
                <span>t</span>
                <span>-</span>
                <span>w</span>
                <span>p</span>
                <span>u</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lower">
            <div class="tail">
                <p>The Computer Society of India (CSI) is a prestigious organization representing computer professionals in India. Established in 1965, CSI boasts a network of 72 chapters, 511 student branches, and over 100,000 members. CSI is dedicated to upholding professional integrity, fostering collaboration, and providing knowledge exchange opportunities.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="main">
        <div class="intro">
            <div class="left">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="wrapper">
                        <div class="banner-image"></div>
                        <h1>Vedangi Thokal</h1>
                        <p>
                            President <br />
                            CSI MIT-WPU
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="button-wrapper">
                        <button class="btn fill">Join Club</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="right">
                <h1>Welcome to the Computer Society of India (CSI-MIT)!</h1>
                <p>Our mission is to advance computer science and IT knowledge across the country. Through dynamic conferences, hands-on workshops, skill-enhancing training programmes, and insightful publications, we aim to empower professionals and students alike. CSI also plays a vital role in bridging the gap between industry and academia, fostering holistic development, and promoting social responsibility in technology.</p>
                <p>With CSI, you can grow in countless ways! Participate in exciting events, enhance your career readiness through recruitment drives and mock placement sessions, and gain invaluable exposure to the tech industry. Whether you’re networking, learning, or exploring, CSI provides opportunities tailored to your growth.</p>
                <p>Join us to explore the world of technology, connect with like-minded individuals, and shape the future of IT in India. We can’t wait to welcome you to the CSI family, where innovation meets opportunity.</p>
                <div class="signature">
                    <h2>President</h2>
                    <h3>CSI</h3>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-intro">
        <h4>Why Join Us?</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="card-containor">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="images/recruitment.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Recruitment</h3>
                <p>Gain access to exclusive recruitment drives with leading companies. CSI provides resume reviews, interview preparation, and connections to help you land internships or full-time roles.</p>
                <a href="" class="btn">Join Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="images/placement.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Mock Placements</h3>
                <p>Prepare for placements with aptitude tests, group discussions, and mock interviews. Receive expert feedback to boost confidence and refine your skills for real-world recruitment scenarios.</p>
                <a href="" class="btn">Enquire Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="images/events.jpeg" alt="">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Events</h3>
                <p>CSI hosts workshops, hackathons, tech fests, and webinars, offering hands-on learning and opportunities to engage with industry experts. These events help you stay updated, showcase your skills, and foster innovation.</p>
                <a href="" class="btn">Enroll Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="js/header.js"></script>
    <script src="js/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>